[h1][b][u]Description[/u][/b][/h1]
[b]Achilles[/b] is a gameplay modification for Arma 3. It expands the Zeus real-time editor with many new additions as well as provides bug fixes.

[b]Achilles[/b] started as an expansion to [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=421908020]Ares[/url] mod, which was created by Anton Struyk. Achilles became the [i]de facto[/i] successor to Ares at the point the latter was no longer updated. Achilles has already grown into a [i]splendid[/i] project, but new additions are still to come! 

