[h1][b][u]Features[/u][/b][/h1]
• Visual changes to the Zeus interface
• Tons of new modules:
　　◦ ACE Medical ([i]e.g.[/i] heal, injury; also work in vanilla!)
　　◦ AI Behaviour ([i]e.g.[/i] animations, garrison buildings, surrender)
　　◦ Arsenal ([i]e.g.[/i] add/modify)
　　◦ Buildings ([i]e.g.[/i] destruction, breachable doors)
　　◦ Development Tools ([i]e.g.[/i] execute code, config/function viewer)
　　◦ Environment ([i]e.g.[/i] advanced weather, earthquakes)
　　◦ Equipment ([i]e.g.[/i] toggle tac light)
　　◦ Fire Support ([i]e.g.[/i] suppressive fire)
　　◦ Objects ([i]e.g.[/i] attach to, toggle simulation, IEDs)
　　◦ Reinforcements ([i]e.g.[/i] spawn reinforcements on the fly)
　　◦ Scenario Flow ([i]e.g.[/i] advanced intel, side relations)
　　◦ Spawn ([i]e.g.[/i] custom compositions, smoke pillar, USS Freedom)
　　◦ Zeus ([i]e.g.[/i] add/remove objects)
• Extended attribute window:
　　◦ Groups ([i]e.g.[/i] careless, hold fire)
　　◦ Vehicles ([i]e.g.[/i] cargo, pylons, garage, damage wheels)
　　◦ [i]etc.[/i]
• New waypoint types:
　　◦ [i]e.g.[/i] seek and destroy, paradrop, sling load
• Hotkeys:
　　◦ Copy/past units including the full loadouts
　　◦ Force unit to pop smoke
　　◦ [i]etc.[/i]
• Customizations:
　　◦ Settings ([i]e.g.[/i] faction filter)

[h1][b][u]Language Localization[/u][/b][/h1]
Achilles is available for the following languages:
• English
• French
• German
• Japanese
• Russian
• Simplified Chinese
• Traditional Chinese
If your language is not on the list, the English localization will be used. New translations are welcome (check out [b]How to Contribute[/b]).

[h1][b][u]Getting Started[/u][/b][/h1]
Below is what you need to know to get Achilles up and running:
• Installing
• Required Addons
• Incompatible Addons
• Optional Addons
• Other Zeus Addons

[u]Installing[/u]
You can download Achilles from:
• [url=https://github.com/ArmaAchilles/AresModAchillesExpansion/releases]GitHub[/url]
• [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=723217262]Steam Workshop[/url]
• [url=http://www.armaholic.com/page.php?id=31235]Armaholic[/url]
If you are not familiar with installing ArmA 3 addons, check out the [url=http://www.armaholic.com/page.php?id=29755]Armaholic installation guide[/url].

[u]Required Addons[/u]
Achilles requires:
• [url=http://arma3.com/]Arma 3[/url]
• [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=450814997]Community Based Addons A3 (CBA_A3)[/url]

[u]Incompatible Addons[/u]
Addons that you should [b]not[/b] run when you use Achilles:
• [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=421908020]Ares[/url]

[u]Optional Addons[/u]
These mods below are required for certain features (e.g. fast-roping):
• [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=463939057]Advanced Combat Environment 3 (ACE3)[/url]
• [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=713709341]Advanced Rappeling (AR)[/url]
• [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=620019431]Task Force Arrowhead Radio (TFAR)[/url]

[u]Other Zeus Addons[/u]
A list of other Zeus mods that are not required, but nice additions:
• [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=642912021]Zeus/Eden Compositions (ZEC)[/url]
• [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=750186990&searchtext=zec]Zeus/Eden Compositions for CUP (ZECCUP)[/url]
• [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1251859358]Zeus/Eden Interiors (ZEI)[/url]

[h1][b][u]Documentation[/u][/b][/h1]
Check out the [url=https://github.com/ArmaAchilles/Achilles/wiki]Achilles Wiki[/url] and the [url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qjD2GX9rCA4&list=PL7del_lBYPTTNEmfPfzKVHxRx8Vx8DxHg]Achilles Tutorial Series on YouTube[/url]. The documentation is rather limited at the time and thus, you will certainly have questions. We will gladly answer them on [url=https://discord.gg/kN7Jnhr]our Discord server[/url].

[h1][b][u]Reporting Issues, Requesting Features and Changes[/u][/b][/h1]
Please use our [url=https://github.com/ArmaAchilles/Achilles/issues]Issue Tracker[/url] for these kinds of purposes.
In the case of a bug report, please only use a minimal set of mods ([i]i.e.[/i] only use other mods than the required ones if they are clearly related to the issue).

[h1][b][u]How to Contribute[/u][/b][/h1]
We always welcome contribution to the repository and thank you for your work! We will update the list of contributors.

What you need to know:
• Basic Steps
• Setting up Your Development Environment
• Add a New Module
• Add a Translation

[u]Basic Steps[/u]
1. [url=https://github.com/ArmaAchilles/Achilles/fork]Fork the Achilles repository[/url]
2. Set up your development Environment
3. Do your stuff
4. [url=https://help.github.com/articles/creating-a-pull-request-from-a-fork/]Create your pull request[/url]
And then we will have a look at your work!

[u]Setting up your local development Environment[/u]
1. [url=https://help.github.com/articles/cloning-a-repository/]Clone your forked repository[/url]
2. Set up your addon builder (either get [url=https://github.com/ArmaAchilles/Hephaestus]Hephaestus[/url] or use the [url=https://github.com/ArmaAchilles/Achilles/blob/master/tools/AchillesAddonBuilder.bat.example ]AchillesAddonBuilder[/url] in the repository)

[u]Add a New Module[/u]
A good starting point for your new module is the [url=https://github.com/ArmaAchilles/Achilles/wiki/Custom-Modules]custom module framework[/url].
We will gladly help you to port your custom module to Achilles (message us on [url=https://discord.gg/kN7Jnhr]our Discord server[/url]).

[u]Add a Translation[/u]
You have to edit the [url=https://github.com/ArmaAchilles/Achilles/blob/master/%40AresModAchillesExpansion/addons/language_f/stringtable.xml]stringtable[/url]. The basics about string tables can be found on the [url=https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/Stringtable.xml]Bohemia Interactive Wiki[/url]. If you don't want to edit the file with a text editor, you can use a dedicated tool such as [url=http://www.armaholic.com/page.php?id=26320]Tabler[/url].

